        "title": "How To Apply Concentrated Attar",
        "heading_size": "h1",
        "subtitle": "LONGEVITY GUIDE",
        "step_1_title": "Dab on Pulse Points",
        "step_1_desc": "Apply your attar to wrists, behind the ears, and inner elbows. These warm areas diffuse the scent beautifully over time.",
        "step_2_title": "Tap Gently, Do Not Rub",
        "step_2_desc": "Gently press your wrists together. Avoid rubbing, as this breaks down the delicate top scent notes and reduces sillage.",
        "step_3_title": "Prep with Moisturizer",
        "step_3_desc": "Fragrance lasts significantly longer on moisturized skin. Apply an unscented moisturizer or lotion to pulse points before dabbing your attar.",
